metadata.name: 𝑴𝒆𝒍𝒂𝒏𝒄𝒐𝒍𝒊𝒂
metadata.description:
Under the moon's melancholic glow, a small figure gazes from below, lost in a vast and endless scene, feeling lonely and sad.

But even in our darkest hour, we hold on tight with all our power for the hope of better days ahead.
We strive to find a glimmer of light, and though we may feel lost and small, we'll rise above it all.

Every bidder will receive an special 1/1 artwork! 

Mixed media with Photoshop digital collage and AI (Midjourney) 
Res. 2000x2800
The buyer will receive a high res. file of the artwork and bidder's edition.
